OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784890079
OL,3,CHow much the government's Summer
OL,4,CSavings scheme has actually helped
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,8,Ftakes a look at the numbers, revealing
OL,9,Fhow much the government's Summer
OL,10,FSavings scheme has helped families
OL,11,Ftaking their children on days out
OL,13,FA Summer Savings scheme run by the
OL,14,Fgovernment was criticised today as not
OL,15,Fgoing far enough.
OL,17,FThe temporary cut in VAT on children's
OL,18,Fmeals and attractions was announced in
OL,19,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
