OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784890079
OL,3,CHow much the government's Summer
OL,4,CSavings scheme has actually helped
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FNow theme parks have told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat the VAT discount has led to more
OL,9,Fcustomers. But to save, families also
OL,10,Fhave to spend.
OL,12,FMother of two Nicola Hoodless is a
OL,13,Fregular visitor to Thorpe Park in
OL,14,FSurrey.
OL,16,FShe said: "It's not just a case of the
OL,17,Fentrance fee, it's the fuel price, the
OL,18,Fmoney for lunch and it all adds up.
OL,19,FI'm looking at easily at least #100
OL,20,Ffor a decent day out."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
