CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784890079
OL,3,CHow much the government's Summer
OL,4,CSavings scheme has actually helped
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FUntil September 1, VAT on children's
OL,8,Fmeals and entry fees to attractions
OL,9,Fsuch as theme parks is cut from 20% to
OL,10,F5%.
OL,12,FOur findings show what that can mean
OL,13,Fon the ground, including 62p off
OL,14,Fchildren's menu pizza at a large pub
OL,15,Fchain, and #4.87 off entry to a major
OL,16,Ftheme park such as Thorpe Park and
OL,17,Ffamily tickets reduced by #3.50 at a
OL,18,Fnational cinema chain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784890079
OL,3,CHow much the government's Summer
OL,4,CSavings scheme has actually helped
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FMany big attractions like Chester Zoo,
OL,8,FTower of London and even Buckingham
OL,9,FPalace visitor centre are not included
OL,10,F` because they are run by charities
OL,11,Fthat don't pay VAT.
OL,13,FThe Vice President of Thorpe Park,
OL,14,FRuth Storey, told us: " We're
OL,15,Fabsolutely delighted about the savings
OL,16,Fscheme. It is something we've been
OL,17,Fasking for a really long time ` and
OL,18,Ffrom the moment it went live we did
OL,19,Factually see an uptick in our online
OL,20,Fsales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784890079
OL,3,CHow much the government's Summer
OL,4,CSavings scheme has actually helped
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"So, we're really happy with the
OL,8,Fperformance so far; it's definitely
OL,9,Fdriving extra visits to the theme
OL,10,Fpark."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FPerhaps surprisingly, food eaten by
OL,18,Fadults can still qualify for discounts
OL,19,Funder the tax scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
