OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784890079
OL,3,CHow much the government's Summer
OL,4,CSavings scheme has actually helped
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThe Blue Stoops restaurant in West
OL,8,FLondon put a meal of wild Burgundy
OL,9,Fsnails on the children's menu.
OL,11,FIt's how the food is marketed that
OL,12,Fcounts, not who actually eats it.
OL,14,FAllen Simpson is a spokesperson for
OL,15,Fthe hospitality trade: "It's only the
OL,16,Fstart, we do need to see the cost of
OL,17,Fhospitality come down even more... but
OL,18,FI hope that at the end of the summer
OL,19,Fthe government will have learned that
OL,20,Fless VAT really does help."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
